<TABLE BORDER=0 cellpadding=4 border=0 cellspacing=1 WIDTH="95%"><TR bgcolor="#D5E6E1"><TD COLSPAN=2><CENTER><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="#000080" FACE="Verdana, Arial">T O P I C  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R E V I E W</font></CENTER></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">modulen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hi all!<P>I'm a little hobbit cleric, which has been fine, until....<P>I just got a faithstone and would like to be able to gate back to rivervale to buy peridots.  Unfortunately, I can't find them anywhere and truly spent fairly little time in rivervale post character creation.<P>Does anywhere know where (if anywhere) in rivervale peridots are sold?  Actually, just knowing they are or aren't sold somewhere could be helpful.  I just don't want to keep looking if there is no hope.  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>Thanks!</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Clenzz</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I think WC is yer closest place to RV there.<P><BR>Just bind in the bazaar.  they sell em there.<P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=171628" TARGET=_blank>Clenzz Teveril</A><BR> <A HREF="http://www.enlighteneddark.org" TARGET=_blank>www.enlighteneddark.org</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Gello</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Peridots aren't sold in RV.  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/frown.gif">  Closest place they're sold is in HHK near the bank.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">modulen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Thanks so much Clenzz and Gello!  That tells me what I wanted to know (even if it isn't what I wanted to hear).  You just saved me hours of searching.  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>Thanks.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">ancarett</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">One helpful solution is to try and keep a full stack (or more) in the bank at all times. Since RV has a bank, you could run by the bank, pick up your dots and gate back. Just make sure you restock fairly frequently.<P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=70555" TARGET=_blank>Ancarett Tourgwin</A>, Veeshan Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Morrun</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">The other place to buy peridots is in EC - there's a collection of 3 huts on the path very close to the WC zone.  One of the vendors (female Erudite IIRC) sells the usual gems, including peridots.<P>Possibly closer to RV than HHK, not sure.<BR><P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=9807" TARGET=_blank>Morrun Catspaw</A><BR>High Priest of Bristlebane<BR>Albion - Death Before Dishonour!<BR>Cazic-Thule Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Fhylden</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I had (have?) the same problem.  Just to be sure, I spent one morning going through every NPC in the vale just to make sure they hadn't hidden peridots on random_npc01.  No luck.  So I sent a /feedback asking to have one added.  If I  am not mistaken, Rivervale is the only cleric faithstone destination without peridots.  Since I'm bound in the nexus, its usefulness isn't nearly as high as it could potentially be.  Ah well, I can still use it to drop down to Antonica without waiting for the spires.<BR><P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=118148" TARGET=_blank>Fhylden daBlanc</A><BR>level 53 Vicar of Bristlebane<BR>Ayonae Ro<BR>Member of &lt;Prism&gt;</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">modulen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Thanks Ancarett, Morrun, and Fhylden!<P>I have pretty much resorted to buying huge stacks of them when I am in other towns and then leaving them in my bank for pick up.  Unfortunately, this means my bank is full, but I guess that is tomorrow's problem.  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>Thanks again!</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Verbannen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Peridots are sold in Kithicor at the inn nearest HHP (loc is about 0,3900.  If you zone out of RV, follow the path to the marker and take the right fork (left leads towards commons), you end up at the inn.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">modulen</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Thanks, Verbannen, that sounds like the way to go!</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
</FONT>
